Let ''A'' be an [[Algebra over a field|algebra]]. A '''comeasuring''' of ''A'' is a pair (''B'',&nbsp;''β'') where:
# ''B'' is an algebra.
# ''β: A → A ⊗ B'' is an [[algebra map]].

